title: 16,714 New York Times Recipes
description:
At http://cooking.nytimes.com/search you may find recipes that the New York Times has helpfully made available. Here are all 16,714 of them; mostly for food but a few for mixed (alcoholic) drinks.

Look inside these HTML files if you want the original URL; if it still works you may be able to see photos. If someone would like to augment this collection with the photos, then re-release it, that would be great.

The 5MB compressed file size means you can email all 16,714 of these recipes to your friends, family, etc.

These are really good recipes. Happy cooking!
